<idea-plugin>
    <id>top.shenluw.intellij.dubbo-plugin</id>
    <name>DubboPlugin</name>
    <vendor email="shenluw@gmail.com" url="https://shenluw.top">Shenluw</vendor>

    <description><![CDATA[
     <h1>dubbo-plug</h1>
    <p>
        <a href="https://996.icu">
            <img src="https://img.shields.io/badge/link-996.icu-red.svg" alt="996.icu">
        </a>
        <a href="https://github.com/996icu/996.ICU/blob/master/LICENSE">
            <img src="https://img.shields.io/badge/license-Anti%20996-blue.svg" alt="LICENSE">
        </a>
    </p>
    <p>dubbo 接口调试插件</p>
    <p>功能：</p>
    <ul>
        <li>
            <p>连接注册中心，获取服务信息</p>
            <p>当前支持 redis, zookeeper, consul</p>
            <p>例如: redis://127.0.0.1:6379?timeout=30000</p>
        </li>
        <li>
            <p>服务接口调用，并发测试</p>
        </li>
    </ul>
    <p>方法参数填写：</p>
    <div>
        <pre>
            <span>接口需要的参数使用yaml语法进行填充</span>
            <span>yaml 一个根对象代表接口需要的一个参数</span>
            <span>如果参数为复杂bean，按照yaml语法创建对象即可</span>
        </pre>
    </div>
    ]]></description>

    <idea-version since-build="171"/>

    <extensions defaultExtensionNs="com.intellij">

        <projectService serviceImplementation="top.shenluw.plugin.dubbo.DubboWindowView"/>
        <projectService serviceImplementation="top.shenluw.plugin.dubbo.DubboStorage"/>
        <projectService serviceImplementation="top.shenluw.plugin.dubbo.UISetting"/>

        <toolWindow id="Dubbo"
                    icon="/icons/dubbo.jpg"
                    anchor="right"
                    secondary="false"
                    factoryClass="top.shenluw.plugin.dubbo.DubboToolWindowFactory"

        >
        </toolWindow>
    </extensions>

    <actions>
    </actions>
</idea-plugin>